        <h6 class="mb-1rem">Fair Information Practices</h6>
        <p class="mb-1rem">The Fair Information Practices Principles form the backbone of privacy law in the United States and the concepts they include have played a significant role in the development of data protection laws around the globe. Understanding the Fair Information Practice Principles and how they should be implemented is critical to comply with the various privacy laws that protect personal information.</p>
        <p class="mb-1rem">In order to be in line with Fair Information Practices we will take the following responsive action, should a data breach occur:</p>
